    <h1>Internal Link</h1>
    <p class="description">A hyperlink from one page on your website to another page on the same domain. Internal links <strong>distribute link equity, build topical authority, and help Google discover and index your content</strong>.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
